summary:
Inspired by these:
Going to the movies with peter (in a au where he can afford to go to the movies) would consist of...
•Lots...
body:
Going to the movies with Peter B. Parker HC

Inspired by these:

Going to the movies with peter (in a au where he can afford to go to the movies) would consist of…

•Lots and Lots of snacks

•Popcorn with extra extra butter

•”we should see that” he says after seeing a really good trailer.

•the worst™️ movie buddy

•probably has a hard time focusing or sitting still

•”that’s not scientifically possible” is some shit he’d whisper during a scene he’s not impressed with

•lots of sushes from other audience members since he can’t shut up

•he somehow always manages to get popcorn crumbs stuck in his suit despite it being spandex and skin tight??

•he’ll hog the snacks without realizing

• you know that moment when you find popcorn in your bra, yeah, he’d probably eat that.

•he’d love hearing about how much you liked the movie and what you liked about the movie, even if he didn’t enjoy it as much he’d still like hearing you talk about it.

•he hates hates hates sitting through the credits, as fore mentioned he can’t sit still, but he’ll do it for you just so you can watch the post-credit scene.

Feel free to add more if you’d like
